metadata.name: Ribbits & Co Black Club Card
metadata.description:
Black Edition Card

Ribbits & Co. Membership Card holders enjoy a wide range of exclusive benefits, including access to captivating Ribbits & Co. generated art pieces and collectibles, exclusive invitations to esteemed web3 industry events, attractive discounts at the Ribbits & Co. online store, and much more as our community expands. 

It is important to note that while these are our current plans and intentions, memberships may be subject to discontinuation at any time due to unforeseen market conditions or other challenges.
